18 service or feature requested for the aspects of
19 the online service or feature with which the
20 minor is actively and knowingly engaged, or
21 (2) the social media platform can demonstrate a
22 compelling reason that profiling does not pose
23 substantial harm or is a privacy risk to minors;
24
